---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Laser Hair Removal | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Long‑term hair reduction for smoother, lower‑maintenance skin.", "canonical": "/services/laser-hair-removal", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px){ .side-col{ display:none; } }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO (left‑aligned, no breadcrumb) -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Laser Hair Removal</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[1.125rem] md:text-xl muted measure">Long‑term hair reduction for smoother, lower‑maintenance skin.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">

    <!-- Removed left side labels entirely -->

    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <!-- DESCRIPTION (unique, professional) -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2>
<p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">Laser hair removal uses concentrated light energy to disable hair follicles and visibly reduce regrowth with minimal downtime. Modern diode, Alexandrite, and Nd:YAG (1064 nm) systems allow safe, effective treatments across a wide range of skin tones.</p>
<p class="mt-3 muted">Compared with shaving or waxing, laser offers precise, long‑term reduction and fewer ingrowns or irritation. Sessions are quick, well‑tolerated, and require little aftercare—so you can return to daily activities right away.</p>
<div class="mt-4 ataglance">
  <span>Series 6–8 sessions</span><span>Minimal downtime</span><span>No waxing between</span><span>Fitzpatrick I–VI</span>
</div>
<p class="pullquote">“Long‑term reduction. Less daily maintenance.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Significant long‑term reduction with finer, lighter regrowth after a full series.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Suitable for a wide range of skin tones (Fitzpatrick I–VI) using modern wavelengths.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Fewer ingrown hairs and less irritation for smoother‑looking skin.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Quick sessions and minimal downtime—no recovery period required.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- THE PROCESS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Consultation</p><p class="muted mt-1">Assessment of goals and medical history, mapping injection points and confirming candidacy.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Treatment</p><p class="muted mt-1">Small injections with a fine needle into targeted muscles; procedure usually takes 10–15 minutes.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Follow‑Up</p><p class="muted mt-1">Results develop in 3–5 days with full effect at 2 weeks. Effects last about 3–4 months.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE / POST (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div><p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2"><li>Avoid tanning/self‑tanners for 2–4 weeks; use daily SPF on the area.</li><li>Shave 24–48 hours before your visit; do not wax, pluck, or use depilatories for 4–6 weeks.</li><li>Pause retinoids/AHAs/BHAs or harsh exfoliants on the area for ~1 week unless advised otherwise.</li><li>Arrive with clean skin—no makeup, lotion, deodorant, or oils on treatment zones.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div><p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2"><li>Expect mild redness/warmth for a few hours; use cool compresses or aloe if needed.</li><li>Avoid heat, sauna, and strenuous exercise for 24 hours; keep the area clean and dry.</li><li>Wear SPF 30+ daily and limit sun exposure for at least one week.</li><li>Do not wax or pluck between sessions; shaving is okay if needed.</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQs (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How is Xeomin different from Botox?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Yes. When performed by trained providers, lasers selectively target hair follicles while minimizing effects on surrounding skin.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">When will I see results?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Most clients need about 6–8 sessions spaced 4–8 weeks apart, depending on area, hair, and goals.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How long do results last?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Most describe a quick snap or warmth. Cooling and modern delivery help keep treatments comfortable.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Is the treatment painful?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Dark hair responds best. With diode/Alexandrite/Nd:YAG options, we can treat a wide range of skin tones safely.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Are there side effects?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Shaving is fine. Avoid waxing, plucking, or depilatories, which remove the follicle the laser needs to target.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- Right margin notes (sticky cues) remain -->
    
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
